    title: "After Your Parent Passes: Adult-Orphan Grief in Your 70s and the Identity Reset",
    excerpt: "She was 96. You are 74. You were her daughter your whole life. Now you are an adult orphan. Here is what to expect and what helps.",
    category: "tips-tricks",
